Special Note from the Author:

Tempo is released under the MIT License to ensure maximum freedom for all users,
especially:

- Small and medium enterprises (PyMEs) competing with tech giants
- Developers in regions with limited internet connectivity
- Medical device manufacturers needing reliable, deterministic systems
- Financial technology innovators democratizing trading

This software is designed to empower those who have been traditionally excluded
from cutting-edge technology. Use it freely, modify it as needed, and build
amazing things that benefit your community.

